## SSH

```powershell
ssh -i C:\path\to\your-key.pem ubuntu@YOUR_PUBLIC_IP
```

User on Canonical Ubuntu images: **`ubuntu`**.

---

## Oracle Cloud — networking checklist

### Security list (subnet)

Ingress (minimum):

| Source | Protocol | Port |
|--------|----------|------|
| Your IP or `0.0.0.0/0` | TCP | 22 |
| `0.0.0.0/0` | TCP | 80 |
| `0.0.0.0/0` | TCP | 443 |

Do **not** expose port **8000** publicly; uvicorn listens on `127.0.0.1:8000` only.

### Ephemeral public IP

Instance → VNIC → primary private IP → assign **ephemeral public IP** if missing.

### Instance iptables (Oracle Ubuntu images)

Default INPUT chain often allows only **22**, then **REJECT** all. Add **80** and **443**:

```bash
sudo iptables -I INPUT 5 -p tcp --dport 80 -j ACCEPT
sudo iptables -I INPUT 6 -p tcp --dport 443 -j ACCEPT
sudo apt install -y iptables-persistent
sudo netfilter-persistent save
```

---

## Server layout

| Path | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `/opt/closet-org` | Git clone, venv, frontend |
| `/opt/closet-org/backend` | FastAPI, `closet.db` |
| `/opt/closet-org/uploads` | Uploaded images (writable by `closet-org`) |
| `/opt/closet-org/.cache` | HF / torch caches |
| `/opt/closet-org/.u2net` | rembg model weights |
| `/etc/closet-org.env` | Production env (mode 600, root) |
| `/etc/systemd/system/closet-org.service` | systemd unit |

Runtime user: **`closet-org`**. Deploy/pull often as **`ubuntu`** or **`root`**, then fix ownership (below).

---

## `/etc/closet-org.env` (example)

```env
CLOSET_ENV=production
CLOSET_SECRET_KEY=PASTE_FROM_python3_-c_import_secrets_print_secrets_token_urlsafe_48
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://YOUR_PUBLIC_IP
TRUST_PROXY_HEADERS=1
UVICORN_RELOAD=0
HOST=127.0.0.1
PORT=8000
HF_HOME=/opt/closet-org/.cache/huggingface
TORCH_HOME=/opt/closet-org/.cache/torch
XDG_CACHE_HOME=/opt/closet-org/.cache
```

**Backup `CLOSET_SECRET_KEY` offline** (password manager). Never commit it.

---

## nginx

Config: `/etc/nginx/sites-available/closet-org`

Required for long uploads / first CLIP classify:

```nginx
proxy_connect_timeout 600s;
proxy_send_timeout 600s;
proxy_read_timeout 600s;
send_timeout 600s;
client_max_body_size 25m;
```

```bash
sudo nginx -t && sudo systemctl reload nginx
```

HTTPS later: `sudo certbot --nginx -d api.yourdomain.com`

---

## Provision / reinstall

Automated script (public repo): `scripts/provision_ubuntu_prod.sh`

```bash
export CLOSET_REPO_URL='https://github.com/YOU/Closet-Org.git'
export PUBLIC_HOSTNAME='YOUR_IP_OR_DOMAIN'
export SKIP_TLS=1   # omit when using certbot + domain

sudo -E bash /path/to/provision_ubuntu_prod.sh
```

Manual reference: `docs/AWS_DEPLOYMENT.md` (same pattern on any Linux VPS).

---

## Deploy code updates

```bash
sudo git config --global --add safe.directory /opt/closet-org
cd /opt/closet-org && sudo git pull

sudo mkdir -p uploads .cache/huggingface .cache/torch .u2net
sudo chown -R closet-org:closet-org backend uploads .venv .cache .u2net

sudo systemctl restart closet-org
```

Static `frontend/` changes do not need a restart; use hard refresh in browser.

