## Web frontend fixes (production)

| Issue | Cause | Fix in repo |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| Choose Image dead | CSP blocks inline `onclick` | `choose-image-btn` + `script.js` listener |
| Upload validation error | Form field must be `files` not `file` | `script.js` |
| `Upload failed: [object Object]` | FastAPI `detail` is JSON array | `formatApiError()` |
| HTML / not JSON on upload | nginx 504 timeout | `proxy_read_timeout 600s` |
| Broken closet thumbnails | DB has `/opt/.../uploads/foo.webp`, `safeUrl` rejected | `closetItemImageUrl()` in `script.js` |

---

## Mobile / Play Store (next)

- `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` = API origin (no trailing slash, no `/api`)
- `eas build --platform android --profile production`
- Google Play one-time fee ~$25
- Prefer **HTTPS + domain** before wide release

